:4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:43:28.000Z","msg":"找換店毒瘤過藥妝金舖，谷貴晒大細舖租<br />\nagent佬搵找換店開天價租唔通又要開咪講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e23ace6e93801b24671f69806f7e48f76e6a615a","tid":1800648,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:44:04.000Z","msg":"好驚俾狗咬而慢慢變返港豬嘅唔該入一入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800681</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8186f5d6a28299313df2bd28e62e79bba0b34c8e","tid":1800648,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:50:11.000Z","msg":"嘩 屌你老味 全旺角拉晒閘竟然仲有一種鋪唔肯拉閘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1707049\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1707049</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}